            <p>本文用於記錄清中（或粵西、廣西）粵語聲母“j”和“nj”對立時各所轄者，但不包括容易寫出漢字的，如「移」「兒」等，此類字聲母大多可由普通話簡單推出。因此，本文主要關注一般不出現在書面語的詞彙。</p>
            <p>下表中，<b>記音</b>列可能有兩列，此時前一列是綜合音，可忽略；本文不寫出師韻 ii（/ɿ/）；<br>
            有些詞可能二聲母皆可，本文不置可否。</p>
            <p><b>字頭</b>列高亮者<b>不</b>代表本字或正字，而只是基於音、義來選出的相對較爲合理的字；併隨後的小號漢字可分別理解爲「優先字形」及「候選字形」；<br>
            <i>斜體者</i>代表該詞可能不出現在現代廣州話中，本文保留作爲參考；<br>
                以「Ｘ」表記的字頭表示本文未對該詞指定優先字形。</p>
            <p>部分詞在不同方言點有讀“nj”也有讀“ng”的，本文兼記。見「<a href="fjb_ng-0">主流粵語聲母 “ng” 與 “0”（零聲母）轄字表</a>」</p>


<table border="1">
<caption>聲母 “j” 與 “nj” 轄字表</caption>
<tr><th style="width: 2.5em;">韻母</th>
    <th style="width: 2.5em;">聲調</th>
    <th style="width: 2.5em;">聲母</th>
    <th colspan="2">記音</th>
    <th style="width: 4em;">字頭</th>
    <th>釋義</th></tr>



    <tr><td rowspan="6">aa</td><td>1</td><td rowspan="2" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njaa1</td><td><i><span class='head'>摣</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①同“揸”：『～條青瓜來喫』；②量詞，一手所抓之量：一～米</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td colspan='2'>njaa3</td><td><i><span class='head'>𠵝</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①食物殘渣⟨壯語：nyaq⟩：甘蔗～；②蠻橫不講理</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">4</td><td rowspan="3" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jaa4</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>炫耀，威風：～文～武</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>jaa4</td><td><i><span class='head'>吔</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>〔～～嗚〕不可靠，不牢靠：『佢啲技術～』</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td colspan='2'>jaa5</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>喏</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>拜祭儀式：拜～(祭拜時的跪拜禮)｜唱～(上香前的默誦行禮）</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td rowspan="3" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njaa6</td><td><span class='head'>廿</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>二十：～四</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">aai</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>njaai1</td><td><i><span class='head'>搋</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'><白>用力揉物：『～了一日嘅面，攰死嘹』</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td colspan='2'>njaai2</td><td><span class='head'>踩</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'><白>踏：～單車</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">3</td><td class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jaai3</td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>物品不結實，鬆散</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njaai3</td><td><i><span class='head'>啀</span><span class='sub'><small>嗌</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>咀嚼⟨壯語：/nyaij，也作“”，越南語：啀/nhai⟩：『啲牛肉太韌嘹，冇～得𧿔』</td></tr>
<tr><td>aak</td><td rowspan="3" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jaak3</td><td><span class='head'>吔</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>同“喫”：～飯</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">aam</td><td colspan='2'>jaam3</td><td><i><span class='head'>湆</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①水慢慢滲漏：『水～出來』｜個隻桶～水；②將物品略溼於水：『～下條手巾』；③以水慢慢 滲入：～花｜～田</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td colspan='2'>jaam5?</td><td><span class='head'>蘸</span><span class='sub'><small>染</small></span></td><td class='mean'>蘸液體、醬或者粉末：『～咗粉先好擰去炸』</td></tr>
<tr><td>aang</td><td rowspan="5">3</td><td class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njaang3</td><td><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>牚</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①艱難地、用力地蹬，運動方向往上：～樓級｜～上山；②大力的踢：『一腳～你出街』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5">aap</td><td class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jaap3</td><td><span class='head'>熠</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>閃爍，閃耀：『燈一～一～』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njaap3</td><td><i><span class='head'>𰞋</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>動詞，生氣⟨壯語：nyapnyuk⟩：發～｜『整到我～澌』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njaap3</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①形容触感粗糙；②形容口感粗糙⟨壯語：nyap⟩</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njaap3</td><td><i><span class='head'>炠</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>刺癢：身～｜～𦢊</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td rowspan="3" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jaap6</td><td><span class='head'>擛</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①鳥的翅膀上下扇動；②柔韌的物品用久後變鬆弛：『個條橡筋～矣』；③蟲子蠕動：『條蟲～來～去』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5">aau</td><td rowspan="8">1</td><td colspan='2'>jaau1</td><td><span class='head'>呦</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔咿咿～～〕不莊重，不正經，草率</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>jaau1</td><td><i><span class='head'>蘨</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'><白>形容翠绿：青～～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njaau1</td><td><span class='head'>爪</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>泛指手：左～</td></tr>
<tr><td>njaau1</td><td><b>(ngaau1)</b></td><td><span class='head'>撓</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'><白>輕抓，搔：～痒</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njaau2<br>njaau1</td><td><i><span class='head'>爪</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'><白>鳥獸的腳：雞～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6">ai</td><td colspan='2'>njai1</td><td><i><span class='head'>搋</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>（用虎口及手指）緊抓：『你～住我做乜？』｜～衫尾</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njai1</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>食嘅肉的俗稱，主要指豬肉：瘦～｜肥～</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njai1</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>用拇指和食指尖掐一點肉：『膠妹好得意，見到就想～～佢䊆面』</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td rowspan="4" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jai4?</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>勩</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>〔～口〕食物口感差</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">5</td><td colspan='2'>jai5</td><td><span class='head'>孈</span><span class='sub'><small>呭</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①膽小；②淘氣：『細細個就咁～』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>jai5</td><td><span class='head'>勩</span><span class='sub'><small>𠯋</small></span></td><td class='mean'>差劣：～嘢｜成績～｜人品～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5">am</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td colspan='2'>jam1</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>陰𩬎</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>劉海：毛～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njam1</td><td><span class='head'>𠰃</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～～笑〕指笑得很開心</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td colspan='2'><b>njam2</b></td><td><span class='head'>飲</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①喝：～水｜～茶｜～酒；②泛指參加酒宴：『一齊去～』</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td colspan='2'>njam3</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>動詞，人在有彈性的物體上上下下跳動， 不停地快速彎曲雙腿使身體上下運動，跳遠前雙腿來回彎曲：『跳遠之前～兩下，跳得遠』</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td colspan='2'>njam6</td><td><span class='head'>任</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>特指因客觀條件不限而隨意：『乜嘢菜都有，～你揀』｜～夠(保夠)</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="8">an</td><td rowspan="3">1</td><td rowspan="2" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jan1</td><td><span class='head'>忻</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～住〕（提醒人）當心：『講埋啲反動嘢，～畀差佬拉去打靶』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>jan1</td><td><i><span class='head'>凐</span><span class='sub'><small>洇</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①寒冷：『近排特別～』；②冷的：『啲水冇識幾～』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2" class="B">nj</td><td>njan1</td><td><b>(ngan1)</b></td><td><i><span class='head'>韌</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>（小孩子）頑皮</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td colspan='2'>njan2</td><td><i><span class='head'>𱭥</span><span class='sub'><small>忍</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>驚顫：𢲜～｜『佢吓到我～一～』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">5</td><td rowspan="2" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jan5</td><td><span class='head'>引</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>導火線</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>jan5</td><td><span class='head'>癮</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>上癮：爛～</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td rowspan="5" class="B">nj</td><td>njan6</td><td><b>(ngan6)</b></td><td><span class='head'>韌</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>易變形而不易斷：『QQ糖好～』</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td>njan4</td><td><b>(ngan4)</b></td><td><i><span class='head'>仁</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>植物的種子</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">ang</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td colspan='2'>njang1</td><td><i><span class='head'>扔</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'><白>牵引，拉：～實實(抓住，亦指糾纏而不善罷甘休)</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njang1</td><td><i><span class='head'>芿</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'><白>①形容雜亂：『頭髮～成一球』｜～蕘蕘；②形容毛髮直立的樣子：雞之毛～</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td colspan='2'>njang3</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>芿</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>牽扯</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5">ap</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td class="A">j</td><td>jap1</td><td><b>jap6<br>jaap6</b></td><td><i><span class='head'>翕</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>招，揮：～手</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njap1</td><td><i><span class='head'>執</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'><白>用指抓取：～菜食</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">4</td><td colspan='2'>njap4</td><td><i><span class='head'>入</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>結賬計數時，算入某人的賬：『～我數』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njap4</td><td><span class='head'>入</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①進，由外到內：～屋；②內：～邊</td></tr>
<tr><td>1</td><td rowspan="6" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jap1<br>jaap3</td><td><span class='head'>熠</span><span class='sub'><small>𥅈𥌅眨</small></span></td><td class='mean'>眨⟨壯語：𥅈，yaep⟩：～眼</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">at</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td colspan='2'>jat1</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>膉</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>水果久置而變質：『隻橙～啊啦，冇食得』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>jat1</td><td><span class='head'>一</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①表選擇：『～你就來～你就冇來』；②表假設：～係｜～冇｜～咪；③重疊形容詞、副詞的強調：紅～紅</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">6</td><td colspan='2'>jat6</td><td><i><span class='head'>逸</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>可愛：『隻狗仔好～』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>jat6</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>逸</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①心情愉悅，高興，快樂：『今日玩得好～啊』；②作動詞，拿人開心：『咪喺度～我啦』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="8">au</td><td rowspan="4">1</td><td colspan='2'>jau1</td><td><span class='head'>憂</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>擔心，擔憂：『我～你冷著』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njau1</td><td><span class='head'>揪</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>用手抓住或扭住：～心</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njau1</td><td><i><span class='head'>搊</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>提起：～褲頭帶</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>njau1</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>形容詞，物體很有韌性，不容易斷的樣子：『好～咬冇入』｜番薯～</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td rowspan="2" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jau2</td><td><span class='head'>𦙓</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔𦣇～〕屁股，臀部</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">3</td><td colspan='2'>jau3</td><td><span class='head'>幼</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①纖細：『支筆寫字好～』；②細膩：～滑</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>njau3</td><td><i><span class='head'>皺</span><span class='sub'><small>𪖐鼼[⿰糹又]</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'><白>皺，起皺⟨壯語：nyaeuq⟩：『條衫～～個』｜～額頭</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td rowspan="3" class="A">j</td><td colspan='2'>jau5</td><td><span class='head'>有</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①存在：『～隻貓撲到在床上』；②表示所屬：『我～一本書』；③發生，產生：『～所得罪』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5">e</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>je1</td><td><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>yeah</small></span></td><td class='mean'>（著裝、打扮）時尚，超前：『渠好～啊』</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td colspan='2'>je4</td><td><span class='head'>爺</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>父親：兩仔～｜〖有～生冇乸教〗</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">5</td><td rowspan="2" class="B">nj</td><td colspan='2'>nje5</td><td><span class='head'>惹</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①招引：『糖會～蟻子』；②染，引致（病）：『佢～一身病』｜『食糖會～痰』；③傳染：『感冒會～人』</td></tr>
